# Test Plan: Membership Checkout Flow (Web Application)

## Objective
Validate that users can successfully purchase a membership without errors across supported browsers and devices.

---

## Scope

### In Scope
- User login
- Membership selection
- Checkout flow
- Payment processing
- Confirmation screen
- Email confirmation trigger

### Out of Scope
- Admin dashboard
- Marketing pages
- Backend payment provider internals

---

## Test Types
- Functional Testing
- Regression Testing
- Exploratory Testing
- Cross-browser Testing
- Negative Testing

---

## Test Scenarios

### Functional
- User can log in successfully
- User can view available membership options
- User can complete checkout with valid payment info
- Confirmation screen displays correct purchase details

### Negative
- Invalid credit card is rejected
- Expired session during checkout
- Missing required fields in checkout form
- Network interruption during payment submission

### Edge Cases
- Double-click submit on payment button
- Browser refresh during checkout
- Switching tabs mid-transaction

---

## Test Data
- Valid user account
- Valid test credit card
- Invalid card numbers (declined, expired)

---

## Exit Criteria
- No P0/P1 defects open
- Payment flow successfully completes across supported browsers
- Confirmation email reliably triggered
